Email2SMS
=========
by Ian Llewellyn

What is it?
-----------
Email2SMS is a daemon like application written in python that listens
for incoming emails on port 25 and, if in the correct format, sends
them via a Siemens M20 GSM modem to the addressed recipient.

Requirements
------------
The application was written in Python 2.6.6 and requires the pySerial
extenstion in order to connect to the RS232 attached GSM modem.
